  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject, AbstractStyle
    public abstract class AbstractStyleImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements AbstractStyle
    An implementation of the model object 'Abstract Style'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Background
    • Foreground
    • Line Width
    • Line Style
    • Filled
    • Line Visible
    • Rendering Style
    • Transparency
